WHEN most people think of their first cars, the idea of a VW Citi Golf, Toyota Tazz or Beetle comes to mind. Well, not unless your parents are rich and famous, then you think differently. It’s no secret that actor and comedian Kevin Hart is an avid, old school car guy – it seems Kevin thought it would be a great idea to surprise his daughter with a brand-new Mercedes-Benz SUV. His daughter, Heaven, received a Mercedes-Benz GLA SUV for her 16th birthday. A post shared by The Shade Room (@theshaderoom) 